sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant Dept as Department System
  participant N8N as n8n/Webhook
  participant Gateway
  participant Adapter as Adapter Runtime
  participant Orch as Orchestration
  participant Case as Case Service
  participant Audit as Audit Service
  participant Kafka
  Dept->>N8N: Status callback
  N8N->>Gateway: Forward signed payload
  Gateway->>Adapter: Verify and normalise
  Adapter->>Orch: Request task transition
  Orch->>Case: Load case/task context
  Orch->>Audit: Record callback transition
  Orch->>Kafka: Publish task/case event
  Orch-->>Gateway: Accepted
  Gateway-->>N8N: 200 OK
